&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting a full time rehabilitation assistant into our Intermediate Care Beds service to enhance the service currently provided by our registered staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for an individual who is passionate about promoting and facilitating independence in older people with complex needs, to allow them to return to their home environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The successful candidate will be dynamic, flexible, enthusiastic, and dedicated to developing themselves within a competency framework.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Access to transport is required, and you must be willing to travel across the Calderdale area.&lt;br /&gt;You may be required to work across 7 days, and to support shift patterns between 08:00 and 16.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
